  <brief_title>Comparison of the Laryngeal Mask Ambu Aura-i Versus AirQ in Children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Comparison of the Pediatric Intubation on Laryngeal Masks Ambu Aira-i and AirQ for Simulated Blind Intubation in Anesthetized Children</official_title>
